    "en": {
      "title": "Amarakirthi murder case; 8 more people were attacked",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Mr. CCTV footage of the killing of three people, including Amarakirthi Athukorala and his security police sergeant, has been released.",
        "The police have sought the public's help in arresting 8 more people identified through these scenes.",
        "Police have released photographs of the eight persons and requested the public to provide information about them to 0112514217 (Director) or 0718592868 (Assistant Director).",
        "35 suspects have been arrested in connection with the incident and most of them have been caught on CCTV. The Police Media Unit further informed that they have been identified through these scenes. has been published."
      ],
